::KitKat::

She kissed him and smiled, "Yes. I shall go into battle with my team 
and we shall be victorios." She got up and stood next to him. She 
winced at her ribs as they slowly healed. She needed a plan of action 
and wanted ehr group assembled to get the plan formulated.  "Call 
Phobia and tell him to get the others together. Then we shall do 
battle."  She put her arm on Drillbit's shoulder and leaned on him as 
her ribs ached.  She was still tired, but the thought of revenge gave 
her strength.
